name: com.castsoftware.uc.slf4j.param
title: Custom environment profile for SLF4J parametrization
description: This extension provides support for the SLF4J logging framework.These parametrization rules will prevent External Link engine (grep tool) to draw Use links towards DB objects whose name are found in argument's strings. Import must be done manually for each Analysis Service (Edit Analysis Service, Select Environment Profile tab, use Import... link at the bottom of the page.
